for this...

this battle is ours!

come from!?

loss without you, adventurer.

cannot hide! We will have ourglory another day!

bigger cookfire this night!

be so strong?

I had hoped for...

all coming from?

They've lured
us into a trap!

The Resistance thanks you.

We march.
You, take the rear guard.

without aught to harvest...?

spared my aunt's whip!

to the Dotharl!

red with your blood!

tails...or on your backs!

them below deck!

Get those blasted
fiends off my ship!

past our forces!?

to watch our rear!

a challenge, and I'm not
about to start!

the moonlight!
Be in awe of my hissatsu!

magitek enhancement!

who might lend me their sword?

your deeds here today, friend.

to come again...

leave this place...

coming with you!

Critical failure...

send me your fists!

all my love with you.

I'll do anything for you.

No one can deny
this love I have inside.

I'll give it all to you─
my endless love!

Rhalgr watch over
and keep you!

hide in plain sight.

eyes─they are everywhere!

everything that
was asked of us!

We are witnesss to ssstrength

You have sssaved our
village! Peace be with you.

the beassstmaid's ssscourge.

There is nothing
more we can do.

sight! Honest!

river in all the land...

crew, ye Red bastards!

away with our bloody rum!

treasures. Run...or stay.

will die here today.

not rest until Yahiro's
blood stains the Ruby red.

Oh ho! A most tasty morsel!
